OL,5, The deputy prime minister has declined 
OL,6, to say whether it was Islamophobic for 
OL,7, Lee Anderson to say London Mayor Sadiq 
OL,8, Khan is controlled by "Islamists".     
OL,10,FOliver Dowden also said Mr Anderson,   
OL,11,Fwho was suspended as a Tory MP after   
OL,12,Frefusing to apologise for the remarks, 
OL,13,Fwould have kept his job if he had.     
OL,15,FHe added that Mr Anderson - a former   
OL,16,Fdeputy Tory chairman - was not         
OL,17,F"intending to be Islamophobic".        
OL,19,FThe comments have provoked a wave of   
OL,20,Fcriticism, including from some Tories. 
